{
  "stem": "27335.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And while waiting there, all of us, you see, nothing to do and so on, and came an alarm in the-- the whole camp.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "A jeep was going around, loud speaker calling my name, Andrew Durovecz, Andrew Durovecz, all around.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I was-- four of us from our troop.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we were on-- on camp duty at-- at-- at-- on the day.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Yeah, because [INAUDIBLE] on, and we'd just done it fast.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was real, real hot on that June day.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And just moved out to the edge of the camp and a lot-- a lot done on the-- the street, [INAUDIBLE] and so on.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And somebody went, hey, they're calling your name.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So-- so what?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I said, oh.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He's coming closer, he's calling my name.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then on the double, in the direction of [INAUDIBLE] we ended up and they were looking for you, come and come, come.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They dragged me into the-- into the jeep and right-- right into the regimental office.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was a colonel.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he laid it down.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was-- it was already-- already-- by that time already, I should have been in Toronto.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But the orderly had misplaced the paper-- they called it paper-- an urgent paper for the colonel when he came back.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "When he was going through the paper, it was in the bottom.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And [INAUDIBLE] and so on to be-- to be discharged from Camp Borden had already been sent into number two district in [INAUDIBLE] to Toronto.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it was already 2 o'clock in the afternoon.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I should have been in Toronto.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He came himself and packed my-- my-- my bag so in the--  in the barrack and-- and fast.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
